    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot? You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute stunner! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life and is in truly pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a worry in sight. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
