    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade A80 chassis powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six. This specimen retains its factory-correct sequential turbocharger configuration, ensuring optimal volumetric efficiency and a linear power band. The drivetrain features the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential, providing exceptional torque bias and mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing double-wishbone architecture with pristine Bilstein dampers. All body panels retain original VIN tags, and the undercarriage exhibits zero oxidation or structural fatigue. The interior is a preservation-class cockpit with functioning instrumentation and original tactile switchgear. This is an unmolested, collector-quality example of the pinnacle of Japanese grand touring performance.",
